1
00:01:41,479 --> 00:01:42,320
Bro.

2
00:01:43,200 --> 00:01:45,200
Bro, something terrible happened.

3
00:01:46,840 --> 00:01:47,280
What's wrong?

4
00:01:47,280 --> 00:01:48,520
Something terrible happened, bro.

5
00:01:48,520 --> 00:01:49,680
Is there a problem with the code?

6
00:01:49,680 --> 00:01:50,640
It's not about your code.

7
00:01:50,640 --> 00:01:52,320
Your code is perfectly written.

8
00:01:52,320 --> 00:01:53,759
It's my mom's colleague's daughter.

9
00:01:53,759 --> 00:01:54,400
She just graduated,

10
00:01:54,400 --> 00:01:55,920
and is coming to Beijing for a job.

11
00:01:55,920 --> 00:01:57,000
She doesn't know her way around here,

12
00:01:57,000 --> 00:01:58,120
so they asked me to look after her.

13
00:01:58,120 --> 00:01:59,479
She's arriving tonight.

14
00:01:59,479 --> 00:02:01,240
I'm so busy with the bidding,

15
00:02:01,240 --> 00:02:02,770
and I really can't get away.

16
00:02:02,920 --> 00:02:05,720
Could you pick her up at the airport for me tonight?

17
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:07,460
Can't you just call a DiDi?

18
00:02:07,600 --> 00:02:08,080
No.

19
00:02:08,360 --> 00:02:09,680
Is she a minor?

20
00:02:11,920 --> 00:02:12,920
No, bro.

21
00:02:13,240 --> 00:02:15,360
This is about my lifelong happiness.

22
00:02:15,680 --> 00:02:16,400
I'm telling you.

23
00:02:16,400 --> 00:02:17,880
Of all the blind dates my mom set me up with,

24
00:02:17,880 --> 00:02:19,610
this one is the most promising.

25
00:02:19,760 --> 00:02:20,890
I've seen her photo.

26
00:02:21,040 --> 00:02:23,240
She's practically a clone of Yui Aragaki.

27
00:02:23,240 --> 00:02:24,300
Most importantly,

28
00:02:24,360 --> 00:02:25,960
she comes from a good family.

29
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:28,000
I have a strong feeling.

30
00:02:29,640 --> 00:02:31,079
I've been single for over twenty years

31
00:02:31,079 --> 00:02:32,640
just to meet her.

32
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:34,480
She is the one for me.

33
00:02:35,720 --> 00:02:37,480
You haven't even seen her in person.

34
00:02:37,480 --> 00:02:38,640
Photos are all fake nowadays.

35
00:02:38,640 --> 00:02:40,000
Don't you know that, bro?

36
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:40,920
Bro.

37
00:02:41,720 --> 00:02:44,520
Even the smallest spark of love can start a prairie fire.

38
00:02:44,520 --> 00:02:46,650
You wouldn't want to kill my happiness

39
00:02:46,760 --> 00:02:48,960
and leave me single forever, would you?

40
00:02:58,480 --> 00:02:59,360
I would.

41
00:02:59,720 --> 00:03:01,240
Don't be heartless.

42
00:03:01,480 --> 00:03:02,940
Brother, I'm begging you.

43
00:03:03,000 --> 00:03:04,000
Just help me out.

44
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:04,800
Please.

45
00:03:04,880 --> 00:03:06,240
This is for my lifelong happiness.

46
00:03:06,240 --> 00:03:07,040
Stop it.

47
00:03:07,040 --> 00:03:08,680
I'm begging you.

48
00:03:08,680 --> 00:03:10,040
Okay.

49
00:03:11,400 --> 00:03:12,060
You agreed.

50
00:03:12,840 --> 00:03:13,700
Let me tell you.

51
00:03:13,720 --> 00:03:14,680
When you go back later,

52
00:03:14,680 --> 00:03:15,720
change into some decent clothes.

53
00:03:15,720 --> 00:03:16,079
No,

54
00:03:16,079 --> 00:03:17,120
do your hair too.

55
00:03:17,200 --> 00:03:18,160
I ordered a bouquet of flowers

56
00:03:18,160 --> 00:03:19,240
to be delivered to your place via Meituan.

57
00:03:19,240 --> 00:03:20,440
Drive my car tonight.

58
00:03:20,840 --> 00:03:22,680
You must make sure her trip to Beijing

59
00:03:22,680 --> 00:03:24,680
leaves a perfect impression on her.

60
00:03:24,800 --> 00:03:25,960
I already bragged to her

61
00:03:25,960 --> 00:03:28,020
that my sidekick would go pick her up.

62
00:03:28,040 --> 00:03:29,079
They say birds of a feather

63
00:03:29,079 --> 00:03:30,010
flock together.

64
00:03:30,240 --> 00:03:31,200
You must leave

65
00:03:31,200 --> 00:03:32,280
a very good impression on her.

66
00:03:32,280 --> 00:03:33,160
Because your image today

67
00:03:33,160 --> 00:03:34,360
represents my image.

68
00:03:35,040 --> 00:03:37,040
It'll raise her expectations of me.

69
00:03:37,760 --> 00:03:39,040
Is that really necessary?

70
00:03:39,040 --> 00:03:39,640
Yes, it is.

71
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:40,600
Of course it does.

72
00:03:40,600 --> 00:03:41,280
Let's go.

73
00:03:41,280 --> 00:03:41,640
Hurry up.

74
00:03:41,640 --> 00:03:42,040
No.

75
00:03:42,040 --> 00:03:43,000
What time?

76
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:44,360
Can I send it to you later?

77
00:03:44,360 --> 00:03:45,560
My phone is still there.

78
00:03:45,560 --> 00:03:46,620
I'll get it for you.

79
00:03:57,840 --> 00:03:58,760
Who is it?

80
00:04:01,960 --> 00:04:03,220
Hello, Daily Flowers.

81
00:04:03,320 --> 00:04:04,850
Is this Mr. Luo Xin's house?

82
00:04:06,040 --> 00:04:07,040
But he's not home.

83
00:04:07,600 --> 00:04:08,600
It's for your family anyway.

84
00:04:08,600 --> 00:04:09,640
Just accept it.

85
00:04:10,440 --> 00:04:11,080
Thank you.

86
00:04:11,680 --> 00:04:12,540
Have a nice day.

87
00:05:01,720 --> 00:05:02,280
Jiangzi.

88
00:05:03,840 --> 00:05:05,770
You paid the utility bills, right?

89
00:05:14,720 --> 00:05:16,450
Why are you back so early today?

90
00:05:17,360 --> 00:05:18,620
I have something to do.

91
00:07:05,120 --> 00:07:05,780
Here we are.

92
00:07:06,440 --> 00:07:07,160
Luo Xin,

93
00:07:07,320 --> 00:07:08,960
thank you for your hospitality today.

94
00:07:08,960 --> 00:07:09,640
You're welcome.

95
00:07:09,640 --> 00:07:11,840
I'm hosting you on behalf of Nie Benjie.

96
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:13,240
How about

97
00:07:13,240 --> 00:07:14,840
you take a picture of me here?

98
00:07:16,240 --> 00:07:17,200
Here too?

99
00:07:17,200 --> 00:07:19,120
You really take photos everywhere you go.

100
00:07:19,120 --> 00:07:20,120
I can't help it.

101
00:07:20,320 --> 00:07:21,650
It's my first time here.

102
00:07:22,200 --> 00:07:23,480
Just use my phone.

103
00:07:24,120 --> 00:07:24,450
Okay.

104
00:07:33,159 --> 00:07:33,490
Okay.

105
00:07:33,680 --> 00:07:34,120
Look.

106
00:07:39,400 --> 00:07:40,520
Oh my god, Luo Xin.

107
00:07:40,760 --> 00:07:43,159
You're really good at taking photos.

108
00:07:43,320 --> 00:07:46,080
You always make me look tall and thin.

109
00:07:47,240 --> 00:07:47,960
Because I have a friend

110
00:07:47,960 --> 00:07:48,960
who works

111
00:07:49,480 --> 00:07:51,340
with photos and videos every day.

112
00:07:51,440 --> 00:07:52,840
I learned from watching.

113
00:07:54,080 --> 00:07:55,240
If someone had

114
00:07:55,240 --> 00:07:57,120
a boyfriend who takes good photos like you,

115
00:07:57,120 --> 00:07:58,450
she would be very happy.

116
00:07:59,840 --> 00:08:00,920
It's getting late.

117
00:08:01,040 --> 00:08:02,400
You should go back and rest.

118
00:08:02,400 --> 00:08:02,840
Okay.

119
00:08:03,120 --> 00:08:04,480
Thank you for today.

120
00:08:04,840 --> 00:08:05,360
Bye.

121
00:09:19,960 --> 00:09:21,090
You're still awake?

122
00:09:21,200 --> 00:09:23,060
You just got back too, didn't you?

123
00:09:28,560 --> 00:09:29,720
121.5.

124
00:09:30,480 --> 00:09:30,960
What?

125
00:09:31,760 --> 00:09:33,360
Your half of the utilities this month.

126
00:09:33,360 --> 00:09:34,760
It's 121.5.

127
00:09:34,920 --> 00:09:35,680
Transfer it to me.

128
00:09:35,680 --> 00:09:37,480
Right now.

129
00:09:38,480 --> 00:09:40,200
You waited until now just for this little amount of money?

130
00:09:40,200 --> 00:09:41,200
Yeah, I'm just that petty.

131
00:09:41,200 --> 00:09:42,260
You just realized?

132
00:09:42,560 --> 00:09:43,960
I don't like owing others.

133
00:09:43,960 --> 00:09:45,760
And I don't like others owing me.

134
00:09:46,000 --> 00:09:46,320
No.

135
00:10:15,200 --> 00:10:17,400
I transferred the money to your WeChat.

136
00:10:36,840 --> 00:10:37,240
Lili.

137
00:10:37,680 --> 00:10:39,200
Ever since you came back from Changde,

138
00:10:39,200 --> 00:10:41,000
I've been wanting to ask you out.

139
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:42,320
I told you.

140
00:10:42,320 --> 00:10:43,920
A clear conscience needs no accuser.

141
00:10:43,920 --> 00:10:44,640
This time,

142
00:10:44,640 --> 00:10:45,360
because of this incident,

143
00:10:45,360 --> 00:10:46,960
you've actually gained a lot of followers.

144
00:10:46,960 --> 00:10:48,080
Eat a lot today.

145
00:10:48,600 --> 00:10:49,400
Piss them off.

146
00:10:50,440 --> 00:10:51,640
Thank you, Xiaoxiao.

147
00:10:52,160 --> 00:10:53,820
No need to be so polite with me.

148
00:10:54,720 --> 00:10:55,240
Oh, right.

149
00:10:55,240 --> 00:10:56,240
I asked you out today

150
00:10:56,240 --> 00:10:57,920
because I have a favor to ask.

151
00:10:58,480 --> 00:10:59,240
What is it?

152
00:10:59,840 --> 00:11:02,360
I opened a Meiduo account, remember?

153
00:11:02,680 --> 00:11:04,120
But I'm a newbie,

154
00:11:04,120 --> 00:11:05,640
so nobody is watching.

155
00:11:05,840 --> 00:11:07,520
So I was hoping you and auntie

156
00:11:07,520 --> 00:11:08,600
could help me record a video

157
00:11:08,600 --> 00:11:09,860
to get me some traffic.

158
00:11:09,960 --> 00:11:10,920
No problem.

159
00:11:10,920 --> 00:11:12,180
When are we recording?

160
00:11:12,240 --> 00:11:13,320
That's great.

161
00:11:13,360 --> 00:11:15,240
I'll let you know once I set a time with her.

162
00:11:15,240 --> 00:11:16,700
Sure, I'm at your service.

163
00:11:17,080 --> 00:11:18,760
This place is really delicious.

164
00:11:18,760 --> 00:11:19,520
Brother Luo Xin,

165
00:11:19,520 --> 00:11:20,560
this is the restaurant.

166
00:11:20,560 --> 00:11:21,120
I'm telling you,

167
00:11:21,120 --> 00:11:22,760
this is currently the most popular restaurant

168
00:11:22,760 --> 00:11:23,720
on Dianping.

169
00:11:24,960 --> 00:11:26,320
Places like this usually have long lines.

170
00:11:26,320 --> 00:11:27,960
I don't know when we'll get to eat.

171
00:11:27,960 --> 00:11:30,090
Don't you have an interview tomorrow?

172
00:11:30,360 --> 00:11:31,040
Only when you're full

173
00:11:31,040 --> 00:11:33,360
will you have the strength to be skinned by capitalists.

174
00:11:33,360 --> 00:11:34,290
Brother Luo Xin,

175
00:11:34,320 --> 00:11:35,450
let's just eat here.

176
00:11:37,880 --> 00:11:39,320
That big bear is so cute.

177
00:11:56,040 --> 00:11:56,570
Jiang Zi.

178
00:11:57,320 --> 00:11:58,040
You're here too.

179
00:11:58,040 --> 00:11:59,170
What a coincidence.

180
00:12:00,320 --> 00:12:01,650
Why are you everywhere?

181
00:12:02,080 --> 00:12:03,440
A friend of mine wants to eat here,

182
00:12:03,440 --> 00:12:05,600
and we don't even know when we'll get a table.

183
00:12:05,600 --> 00:12:06,930
Lili, is he your friend?

184
00:12:08,200 --> 00:12:08,840
Sort of.

185
00:12:09,240 --> 00:12:09,640
Hello.

186
00:12:11,600 --> 00:12:13,880
Is he the faceless guy in your videos?

187
00:12:15,120 --> 00:12:18,120
This lady looks very familiar.

188
00:12:23,400 --> 00:12:24,400
Jiang Zi.

189
00:12:24,960 --> 00:12:26,820
You are the influencer, Jiang Zi.

190
00:12:27,240 --> 00:12:28,120
Brother Luo Xin,

191
00:12:28,120 --> 00:12:29,040
why didn't you tell me

192
00:12:29,040 --> 00:12:31,100
that your friend is a big influencer?

193
00:12:33,640 --> 00:12:34,560
Sister Jiang Zi,

194
00:12:34,560 --> 00:12:36,520
I've seen your video about living in Beijing.

195
00:12:36,520 --> 00:12:38,720
I really think you are strong and brave.

196
00:12:38,840 --> 00:12:40,040
Because when I think about it,

197
00:12:40,040 --> 00:12:41,320
if I were nearly thirty

198
00:12:41,520 --> 00:12:43,640
and still drifting alone in Beijing,

199
00:12:43,960 --> 00:12:45,820
I would have broken down long ago.

200
00:12:46,080 --> 00:12:46,880
So I really think

201
00:12:46,880 --> 00:12:47,810
you're amazing.

202
00:12:47,920 --> 00:12:49,080
And seeing you today,

203
00:12:49,080 --> 00:12:50,640
your face is so small.

204
00:12:50,840 --> 00:12:53,570
You look much better in person than in the videos.

205
00:12:53,640 --> 00:12:54,680
Thank you.

206
00:12:54,680 --> 00:12:55,140
Ziqian,

207
00:12:55,680 --> 00:12:56,610
let's go line up.

208
00:12:57,640 --> 00:12:59,120
Since you are Lili's friend,

209
00:12:59,120 --> 00:13:00,450
sit down and eat with us.

210
00:13:00,480 --> 00:13:01,120
Really?

211
00:13:01,560 --> 00:13:03,000
Thank you, that's great.

212
00:13:03,000 --> 00:13:03,640
Brother Luo Xin,

213
00:13:03,640 --> 00:13:04,120
come in.

214
00:13:06,200 --> 00:13:08,000
What are you standing there for?

215
00:13:08,600 --> 00:13:09,360
Come in.

216
00:13:09,560 --> 00:13:10,640
We are all friends.

217
00:13:10,680 --> 00:13:12,160
This way we don't have to wait in line.

218
00:13:12,160 --> 00:13:13,520
Why are you getting shy?

219
00:13:13,800 --> 00:13:14,460
Have a seat.

220
00:13:15,080 --> 00:13:15,720
Waiter.

221
00:13:20,280 --> 00:13:21,680
Two more steaks, please.

222
00:13:22,400 --> 00:13:24,730
Okay, how would you like your steaks done?

223
00:13:25,520 --> 00:13:26,250
Medium well.

224
00:13:27,280 --> 00:13:28,720
Medium for me, thanks.

225
00:13:28,760 --> 00:13:30,290
Okay, please wait a moment.

226
00:13:33,600 --> 00:13:35,760
Medium steaks have higher nutritional value.

227
00:13:35,760 --> 00:13:37,160
The key is that it's tender.

228
00:13:37,160 --> 00:13:38,960
Yes, and the texture is good too.

229
00:13:42,320 --> 00:13:43,780
I'm going to the restroom.

230
00:13:52,000 --> 00:13:52,640
Hey,

231
00:13:53,040 --> 00:13:54,240
You are so pretty too.

232
00:13:54,360 --> 00:13:55,890
Are you also an influencer?

233
00:13:56,200 --> 00:13:57,680
Not exactly.

234
00:13:57,680 --> 00:13:59,960
I'm telling you, you'd definitely go viral as an influencer.

235
00:13:59,960 --> 00:14:00,560
Thank you.

236
00:14:00,960 --> 00:14:03,160
Do you have an account? I can follow you.

237
00:14:03,360 --> 00:14:03,720
Sure.

238
00:14:33,520 --> 00:14:34,050
Jiangzi.

239
00:14:34,640 --> 00:14:35,240
What is it?

240
00:14:38,000 --> 00:14:40,460
How much was dinner? I'll transfer it to you.

241
00:14:42,280 --> 00:14:44,600
Do you really like settling accounts with me this much?

242
00:14:44,600 --> 00:14:45,400
Didn't you say

243
00:14:45,400 --> 00:14:47,200
you don't like people owing you?

244
00:14:51,240 --> 00:14:52,200
1,100 in total.

245
00:14:52,200 --> 00:14:54,000
You and your girlfriend owe 550.

246
00:14:54,240 --> 00:14:55,400
No, she's not my girlfriend.

247
00:14:55,400 --> 00:14:56,640
Is she 'not yet' your girlfriend,

248
00:14:56,640 --> 00:14:58,100
or 'not' your girlfriend?

249
00:15:00,360 --> 00:15:01,360
Keep pretending.

250
00:15:01,960 --> 00:15:02,280
No.

251
00:15:04,800 --> 00:15:05,330
Pervert.

252
00:15:23,920 --> 00:15:24,880
What's wrong?

253
00:15:36,120 --> 00:15:37,120
You're here, bro.

254
00:15:38,640 --> 00:15:39,680
Returning her to you.

255
00:15:39,680 --> 00:15:41,010
Mission accomplished.

256
00:15:41,440 --> 00:15:43,120
Ziqian just WeChatted me.

257
00:15:43,680 --> 00:15:45,600
Thanks for hosting her these past two days.

258
00:15:45,600 --> 00:15:46,130
Tonight,

259
00:15:46,280 --> 00:15:47,880
she's treating us to dinner.

260
00:15:48,440 --> 00:15:49,500
You go by yourself.

261
00:15:50,760 --> 00:15:52,000
You're all good now,

262
00:15:52,720 --> 00:15:53,780
but I'm miserable.

263
00:15:55,040 --> 00:15:56,160
What's going on?

264
00:15:58,400 --> 00:15:59,160
Jiangzi

265
00:15:59,160 --> 00:16:01,360
seems to have misunderstood my relationship with her.

266
00:16:01,360 --> 00:16:03,690
She hasn't given me a good look in two days.

267
00:16:04,120 --> 00:16:05,680
Then just explain it to her.

268
00:16:06,160 --> 00:16:06,840
I did.

269
00:16:06,840 --> 00:16:07,840
She won't listen.

270
00:16:12,360 --> 00:16:13,420
Wait a minute, bro.

271
00:16:15,560 --> 00:16:16,120
No.

272
00:16:18,760 --> 00:16:20,400
This means you have a chance.

273
00:16:21,480 --> 00:16:23,410
The little influencer is jealous.

274
00:16:31,240 --> 00:16:31,960
She...

275
00:16:34,240 --> 00:16:35,600
likes me.

276
00:16:37,360 --> 00:16:37,800
Right.

277
00:16:40,160 --> 00:16:42,160
Have you ever watched Animal World?

278
00:16:42,400 --> 00:16:44,720
A male lion chases a lioness,

279
00:16:45,200 --> 00:16:47,120
and the lioness ignores him.

280
00:16:47,680 --> 00:16:50,040
If another lioness appears,

281
00:16:50,960 --> 00:16:53,360
they will immediately fight over the male.

282
00:16:54,080 --> 00:16:55,760
This is animal instinct.

283
00:16:57,840 --> 00:17:00,500
Aren't you always worried she won't accept you?

284
00:17:00,720 --> 00:17:01,440
If I were you,

285
00:17:01,440 --> 00:17:03,200
I'd use this misunderstanding,

286
00:17:03,200 --> 00:17:04,440
take the initiative,

287
00:17:05,000 --> 00:17:06,400
and make her chase you.

288
00:17:27,400 --> 00:17:28,930
Welcome back to my channel.

289
00:17:28,960 --> 00:17:30,620
Hello everyone, I'm Jiangzi.

290
00:17:31,640 --> 00:17:34,360
A lot has happened to me recently,

291
00:17:34,440 --> 00:17:36,440
so I haven't updated for over a week.

292
00:17:37,120 --> 00:17:38,880
Now I'm back with full energy.

293
00:17:38,880 --> 00:17:40,440
Jiangzi is still Jiangzi.

294
00:17:40,880 --> 00:17:42,480
I will continue to make

295
00:17:42,480 --> 00:17:44,000
more and better content for you.

296
00:17:44,000 --> 00:17:46,130
I hope you will continue to support me.

297
00:18:50,880 --> 00:18:51,920
Why are you here?

298
00:18:53,840 --> 00:18:55,320
I was running errands nearby,

299
00:18:55,320 --> 00:18:56,080
passing by,

300
00:18:56,520 --> 00:18:57,380
and thought I'd

301
00:18:57,680 --> 00:18:59,880
pick you up so we could go back together.

302
00:19:00,040 --> 00:19:00,640
No need.

303
00:19:23,000 --> 00:19:24,800
It snowed quite early this year.

304
00:19:53,600 --> 00:19:54,240
Jiang Zi.

305
00:19:56,840 --> 00:19:57,880
What do you think

306
00:19:58,960 --> 00:20:00,690
our relationship is right now?

307
00:20:12,640 --> 00:20:13,600
Duh.

308
00:20:14,080 --> 00:20:15,280
Comrades, of course.

309
00:20:16,480 --> 00:20:17,760
I think so too.

310
00:20:22,320 --> 00:20:24,160
I recently fell for a girl.

311
00:20:27,320 --> 00:20:29,380
But I don't know how to make her happy.

312
00:20:30,720 --> 00:20:31,850
Give me some advice.

313
00:20:33,920 --> 00:20:35,720
I think you're pretty good at it.

314
00:20:36,120 --> 00:20:37,040
You give her flowers,

315
00:20:37,040 --> 00:20:38,360
take her to trendy restaurants,

316
00:20:38,360 --> 00:20:39,890
and take nice photos of her.

317
00:20:42,880 --> 00:20:44,280
What else besides those?

318
00:20:46,600 --> 00:20:47,520
How would I know?

319
00:20:47,520 --> 00:20:49,380
If you like her, ask her yourself.

320
00:21:00,880 --> 00:21:02,280
I'm asking her right now.

321
00:21:14,320 --> 00:21:15,120
Jiang Zi,

322
00:21:19,240 --> 00:21:19,960
I like you.

323
00:21:38,040 --> 00:21:39,640
I don't know since when,

324
00:21:42,120 --> 00:21:43,520
the way you look unkempt,

325
00:21:44,760 --> 00:21:46,820
the way you haggle over every detail,

326
00:21:47,360 --> 00:21:49,040
the way you desperately shoot videos,

327
00:21:49,040 --> 00:21:49,900
I like them all.

328
00:21:53,080 --> 00:21:54,840
But I don't want to be someone

329
00:21:54,840 --> 00:21:56,960
you consider fine after careful thought.

330
00:21:56,960 --> 00:21:58,360
Nor do I want to be someone

331
00:21:58,360 --> 00:21:59,890
you snatch out of jealousy.

332
00:22:01,360 --> 00:22:02,760
I really hope to be

333
00:22:03,320 --> 00:22:04,980
someone who moves your heart,

334
00:22:05,160 --> 00:22:06,420
someone you can trust,

335
00:22:08,000 --> 00:22:09,530
and someone you can rely on.

336
00:22:13,280 --> 00:22:13,880
Of course,

337
00:22:14,560 --> 00:22:16,400
you don't have to answer me in a hurry.

338
00:22:16,400 --> 00:22:18,120
When you've thought it through,

339
00:22:18,120 --> 00:22:18,800
tell me.

340
00:22:19,520 --> 00:22:21,180
I live right next door anyway.

341
00:22:24,200 --> 00:22:26,040
Then what about Yuan Ziqian?

342
00:22:37,960 --> 00:22:38,360
Look.

343
00:22:39,480 --> 00:22:40,000
This

344
00:22:40,760 --> 00:22:43,080
is our contact tracing data for the past two days.

345
00:22:43,080 --> 00:22:44,540
It's captured by big data,

346
00:22:44,840 --> 00:22:46,900
absolutely objective and credible.

347
00:22:47,800 --> 00:22:49,920
Besides, she is just someone from my colleague's hometown.

348
00:22:49,920 --> 00:22:51,520
She has nothing to do with me.

349
00:22:54,640 --> 00:22:56,570
Then why didn't you say so earlier?

350
00:22:59,360 --> 00:23:00,120
Earlier,

351
00:23:01,920 --> 00:23:04,000
I didn't know how you would respond.

352
00:23:08,280 --> 00:23:10,810
Then how do you think I will respond to you now?

353
00:24:20,960 --> 00:24:21,480
Mr. Lu.

354
00:24:23,320 --> 00:24:25,160
When I was signing the contract with Mr. Chen just now,

355
00:24:25,160 --> 00:24:26,160
didn't you see him?

356
00:24:26,160 --> 00:24:27,880
You didn't even come over to say hello.

357
00:24:27,880 --> 00:24:28,800
Taking a dump.

358
00:24:28,960 --> 00:24:29,520
No time.

359
00:24:31,440 --> 00:24:33,400
You just lost a small deal.

360
00:24:33,400 --> 00:24:34,480
Why the long face?

361
00:24:36,680 --> 00:24:37,840
You just got lucky.

362
00:24:38,120 --> 00:24:39,120
It's just a fluke.

363
00:24:39,440 --> 00:24:40,880
There's no need to attribute everything

364
00:24:40,880 --> 00:24:42,520
to good and bad luck.

365
00:24:44,640 --> 00:24:45,280
Luck?

366
00:24:45,920 --> 00:24:47,250
Like hell I believe you.

367
00:25:09,880 --> 00:25:10,640
Cheers!

368
00:25:11,480 --> 00:25:12,000
Cheers!

369
00:25:13,720 --> 00:25:15,320
What are they so happy about?

370
00:25:19,720 --> 00:25:20,520
Hello, Mr. Li.

371
00:25:21,800 --> 00:25:22,930
You must be Jiangzi.

372
00:25:24,400 --> 00:25:25,330
This time, Aiwei

373
00:25:25,960 --> 00:25:27,760
took a big risk for you.

374
00:25:28,560 --> 00:25:29,640
What happened

375
00:25:29,680 --> 00:25:30,320
to Aiwei?

376
00:25:31,000 --> 00:25:32,000
Here's the thing.

377
00:25:32,120 --> 00:25:33,320
After your accident,

378
00:25:33,720 --> 00:25:34,650
Meiduo proposed

379
00:25:35,200 --> 00:25:35,960
removing you from

380
00:25:35,960 --> 00:25:37,960
the Chunyan Project list,

381
00:25:38,400 --> 00:25:40,440
or else they would terminate the cooperation.

382
00:25:40,440 --> 00:25:42,240
It was Aiwei who vouched for you.

383
00:25:42,440 --> 00:25:43,300
And she managed

384
00:25:43,560 --> 00:25:44,640
to get them

385
00:25:44,800 --> 00:25:46,480
to give us a three-day buffer.

386
00:25:49,520 --> 00:25:50,920
Losing this cooperation

387
00:25:51,400 --> 00:25:52,680
would be an incalculable loss for Aiwei

388
00:25:52,680 --> 00:25:54,080
and our company,

389
00:25:54,080 --> 00:25:55,720
One Thousand and One Nights.

390
00:25:57,480 --> 00:25:58,880
Keep making good videos.

391
00:25:58,880 --> 00:26:00,610
I'll visit your channel often.

392
00:26:01,120 --> 00:26:02,000
Thank you, Mr. Li.

393
00:26:02,000 --> 00:26:02,960
Hello, Mr. Li.

394
00:26:03,040 --> 00:26:04,040
We are ready here.

395
00:26:04,680 --> 00:26:05,940
You can go back to work.

396
00:26:15,920 --> 00:26:17,680
My dear colleagues,

397
00:26:18,040 --> 00:26:19,360
Good evening.

398
00:26:26,600 --> 00:26:28,260
After months of competition,

399
00:26:29,440 --> 00:26:30,080
today,

400
00:26:30,280 --> 00:26:31,680
I am here to announce

401
00:26:31,960 --> 00:26:34,490
the recipient of our 200 million investment.

402
00:26:35,640 --> 00:26:39,040
Based on the network-wide traffic statistics from Migu Data

403
00:26:39,160 --> 00:26:41,520
and the work performance over the past six months,

404
00:26:41,520 --> 00:26:44,180
the board of directors has unanimously decided

405
00:26:45,000 --> 00:26:47,200
that the 200 million investment goes to

406
00:26:47,880 --> 00:26:50,210
Aiwei and her One Thousand and One Nights.

407
00:26:54,440 --> 00:26:56,360
We're rich! We're rich!

408
00:26:56,400 --> 00:26:59,240
We're rich! We're rich! We're rich!

409
00:27:09,000 --> 00:27:11,000
Aiwei is our Shengshi Company's

410
00:27:11,000 --> 00:27:12,730
top professional influencer.

411
00:27:12,760 --> 00:27:15,360
Not only has she made a successful transition,

412
00:27:15,480 --> 00:27:16,800
but her live-streaming business

413
00:27:16,800 --> 00:27:18,160
is also booming.

414
00:27:18,800 --> 00:27:20,720
Aiwei even had the Midas touch,

415
00:27:20,760 --> 00:27:22,240
teaming up with Meiduo.

416
00:27:22,640 --> 00:27:24,040
The Spring Goose Project

417
00:27:24,440 --> 00:27:26,800
has cultivated

418
00:27:27,040 --> 00:27:28,960
rising stars of tomorrow like Jiang Zi.

419
00:27:28,960 --> 00:27:29,560
Thank you.

420
00:27:33,880 --> 00:27:35,520
We hope this investment

421
00:27:35,800 --> 00:27:38,200
will help One Thousand and One Nights

422
00:27:38,200 --> 00:27:39,560
achieve even greater success

423
00:27:39,560 --> 00:27:41,420
and reach the top of our industry.

424
00:27:41,640 --> 00:27:42,800
Great.

425
00:27:43,760 --> 00:27:45,960
Congratulations on the championship.

426
00:27:48,680 --> 00:27:51,320
Let's invite Ms. Ai Wei to the stage to say a few words.

427
00:27:51,320 --> 00:27:52,080
Welcome,

428
00:27:56,240 --> 00:27:58,520
Ai Wei.

429
00:27:58,520 --> 00:28:00,720
Ai Wei.

430
00:28:03,280 --> 00:28:04,320
Thank you, Mr. Li.

431
00:28:05,240 --> 00:28:06,120
Congratulations.

432
00:28:06,120 --> 00:28:07,480
Thank you, Mr. Li.

433
00:28:07,720 --> 00:28:08,520
Well,

434
00:28:09,080 --> 00:28:11,520
to be able to secure this 200 million investment,

435
00:28:11,520 --> 00:28:13,160
first and foremost, I must thank

436
00:28:13,160 --> 00:28:16,290
the board of directors for their support and trust in me.

437
00:28:16,680 --> 00:28:18,080
But most importantly,

438
00:28:18,520 --> 00:28:20,800
I want to thank my colleagues

439
00:28:21,120 --> 00:28:22,080
and my team.

440
00:28:22,640 --> 00:28:26,040
It is because of your unremitting efforts and perseverance

441
00:28:26,040 --> 00:28:28,280
that we have created the grand and beautiful fairytale

442
00:28:28,280 --> 00:28:31,240
of One Thousand and One Nights.

443
00:28:31,480 --> 00:28:32,320
So,

444
00:28:32,520 --> 00:28:33,560
tonight's honor

445
00:28:34,600 --> 00:28:35,800
belongs to all of you.

446
00:28:36,600 --> 00:28:38,720
Please cheer for yourselves.

447
00:28:52,920 --> 00:28:53,480
I know.

448
00:28:53,760 --> 00:28:54,440
A while ago,

449
00:28:54,440 --> 00:28:56,680
you two were fighting fiercely.

450
00:28:57,640 --> 00:28:59,760
As for the allocation of this investment,

451
00:28:59,760 --> 00:29:02,020
it was a unanimous decision by the board.

452
00:29:02,600 --> 00:29:03,280
Besides,

453
00:29:03,280 --> 00:29:05,080
promoting one company to the top

454
00:29:05,080 --> 00:29:06,440
is the general trend.

455
00:29:08,640 --> 00:29:10,440
Let's put this matter behind us.

456
00:29:10,600 --> 00:29:11,240
No matter what,

457
00:29:11,240 --> 00:29:12,840
we are in the same company,

458
00:29:12,880 --> 00:29:14,280
and our interests align.

459
00:29:14,960 --> 00:29:16,090
Let's drink to that.

460
00:29:18,040 --> 00:29:20,200
There is no progress without competition.

461
00:29:20,200 --> 00:29:21,240
I understand that much.

462
00:29:21,240 --> 00:29:23,080
Anyway, through this experience,

463
00:29:23,080 --> 00:29:24,480
I feel I've learned a lot,

464
00:29:24,640 --> 00:29:27,240
and One Thousand and One Nights has grown a lot.

465
00:29:27,360 --> 00:29:28,520
I should also thank Mr. Lu.

466
00:29:28,520 --> 00:29:30,720
I'll treat you to dinner some other day.

467
00:29:32,640 --> 00:29:33,100
Cheers.

468
00:29:42,120 --> 00:29:42,680
Lili.

469
00:29:42,680 --> 00:29:44,210
Xiaoxiao, you're here too.

470
00:29:44,520 --> 00:29:45,680
It's my aunt's celebration party.

471
00:29:45,680 --> 00:29:46,600
I definitely had to come.

472
00:29:46,600 --> 00:29:47,040
Yeah.

473
00:29:47,040 --> 00:29:49,320
Aiwei has really put in a lot for today.

474
00:29:50,800 --> 00:29:51,160
By the way,

475
00:29:51,160 --> 00:29:52,320
I made an appointment with my aunt

476
00:29:52,320 --> 00:29:54,450
to shoot a video for me tomorrow night.

477
00:29:54,600 --> 00:29:55,560
I wonder if a busy person like you

478
00:29:55,560 --> 00:29:56,360
has time.

479
00:29:56,920 --> 00:29:58,280
Of course.

480
00:29:58,280 --> 00:29:59,160
I'm available anytime.

481
00:29:59,160 --> 00:30:00,040
That's great.

482
00:30:01,880 --> 00:30:02,410
Jiangzi.

483
00:30:03,240 --> 00:30:04,880
These friends of mine are your fans.

484
00:30:04,880 --> 00:30:06,960
They'd like to take a picture with you. I wonder

485
00:30:06,960 --> 00:30:07,280
if it's convenient.

486
00:30:07,280 --> 00:30:08,800
No problem. Where should we shoot?

487
00:30:08,800 --> 00:30:09,240
Here.

488
00:30:09,240 --> 00:30:10,000
Let's take it here.

489
00:30:10,000 --> 00:30:10,440
Sure.

490
00:30:10,440 --> 00:30:11,900
Come, I'll take it for you.

491
00:30:13,320 --> 00:30:14,680
Everyone, look at me.

492
00:30:14,920 --> 00:30:16,880
Three, two, one,

493
00:30:16,880 --> 00:30:18,120
cheese.

494
00:30:18,400 --> 00:30:19,480
Come, let's take a picture together.

495
00:30:19,480 --> 00:30:19,920
Okay.

496
00:30:20,040 --> 00:30:20,640
Come here.

497
00:30:20,760 --> 00:30:21,120
Come.

498
00:30:21,480 --> 00:30:23,400
One, two, three, cheese.

499
00:30:23,400 --> 00:30:24,280
Let's take another one.

500
00:30:24,280 --> 00:30:25,680
One, two, three, cheese.

501
00:30:26,120 --> 00:30:27,480
Let's look at the picture,

502
00:30:27,480 --> 00:30:28,540
to see if it's good.

503
00:30:29,120 --> 00:30:30,160
It looks so good.

504
00:30:30,320 --> 00:30:30,780
Not bad.

505
00:30:33,560 --> 00:30:34,520
Excuse me.

506
00:30:34,680 --> 00:30:35,400
Sorry.

507
00:30:37,280 --> 00:30:37,880
Xiaoxiao.

508
00:30:39,560 --> 00:30:40,280
Auntie.

509
00:30:44,240 --> 00:30:46,120
Ai Wei gave you the cold shoulder,

510
00:30:46,720 --> 00:30:48,720
and her niece is pulling the same stunt.

511
00:30:48,720 --> 00:30:49,440
I think

512
00:30:49,440 --> 00:30:50,900
she's doing it on purpose.

513
00:30:54,080 --> 00:30:55,120
Ai Wei's niece?

514
00:30:55,760 --> 00:30:56,200
Yeah.

515
00:30:56,760 --> 00:30:58,560
I've seen her at the company a few times.

516
00:30:58,560 --> 00:30:59,960
Her name is Lin Xiaoxiao.

517
00:31:00,600 --> 00:31:01,760
I heard Ai Wei treats her

518
00:31:01,760 --> 00:31:03,240
like her own daughter.

519
00:31:07,120 --> 00:31:07,920
Lin Xiaoxiao.

520
00:31:10,520 --> 00:31:11,050
Let's go.

521
00:31:26,640 --> 00:31:27,500
I just got home.

522
00:31:30,200 --> 00:31:30,800
What is it?

523
00:31:34,280 --> 00:31:34,800
No.

524
00:31:35,200 --> 00:31:36,320
I told you a long time ago.

525
00:31:36,320 --> 00:31:39,050
Stop looking for these unreliable investments.

526
00:31:39,480 --> 00:31:41,140
How is it different this time?

527
00:31:45,360 --> 00:31:46,420
What are you doing?

528
00:31:47,160 --> 00:31:48,020
Hanging up now.

529
00:31:48,360 --> 00:31:49,890
I didn't know you were back.

530
00:31:50,400 --> 00:31:51,040
Well...

531
00:31:51,320 --> 00:31:52,000
I'm nearsighted.

532
00:31:52,000 --> 00:31:53,260
I didn't see anything.

533
00:32:10,040 --> 00:32:11,900
Luo Xin, the bathroom is free now.

534
00:32:34,880 --> 00:32:36,480
Jiangzi, what are you doing?

535
00:32:37,040 --> 00:32:38,960
I didn't see anything either.

536
00:33:44,040 --> 00:33:44,920
Rest early.

537
00:33:46,560 --> 00:33:47,600
You have a follow-up visit tomorrow.

538
00:33:47,600 --> 00:33:48,600
It should be fine.

539
00:33:53,240 --> 00:33:54,700
What do you mean 'should'?

540
00:33:56,960 --> 00:33:59,220
You should've ended the stream earlier.

541
00:34:00,400 --> 00:34:02,360
My hand wouldn't be like this.

542
00:34:13,199 --> 00:34:15,120
I have a very important meeting tomorrow morning.

543
00:34:15,120 --> 00:34:15,800
After the meeting,

544
00:34:15,800 --> 00:34:18,199
I'll come back and take you to the hospital.

545
00:34:24,400 --> 00:34:26,000
I wouldn't dare trouble you.

546
00:34:27,840 --> 00:34:29,280
You're a busy person.

547
00:35:11,080 --> 00:35:12,340
How does the hand feel?

548
00:35:12,960 --> 00:35:14,760
It really doesn't hurt anymore.

549
00:35:15,000 --> 00:35:15,860
It's just that,

550
00:35:16,400 --> 00:35:16,920
look,

551
00:35:18,160 --> 00:35:21,360
I still can't use any strength in my ring and little fingers.

552
00:35:21,360 --> 00:35:23,040
I've had two courses of treatment.

553
00:35:23,040 --> 00:35:23,770
Why hasn't it

554
00:35:25,320 --> 00:35:26,850
completely recovered yet?

555
00:35:27,920 --> 00:35:30,320
I'm afraid this is already the best result.

556
00:35:33,720 --> 00:35:34,650
What did you say?

557
00:35:36,360 --> 00:35:37,160
After two courses of treatment,

558
00:35:37,160 --> 00:35:38,800
the fact that your hand has recovered to this extent

559
00:35:38,800 --> 00:35:40,360
is already the best result.

560
00:35:48,240 --> 00:35:48,840
Dr. Sun.

561
00:35:50,640 --> 00:35:53,640
I will continue to actively cooperate with your treatment.

562
00:35:53,640 --> 00:35:54,970
I can do another course,

563
00:35:56,040 --> 00:35:56,700
or even two.

564
00:35:56,720 --> 00:35:57,360
No.

565
00:35:57,360 --> 00:35:58,890
Mr. Chen, here is the thing.

566
00:35:59,520 --> 00:36:01,720
Basically, the result you get after two courses

567
00:36:01,720 --> 00:36:03,250
is already the best result.

568
00:36:03,600 --> 00:36:04,960
Doing a few more courses

569
00:36:05,520 --> 00:36:07,320
won't make much of a difference.

570
00:36:14,600 --> 00:36:15,520
But Dr. Sun,

571
00:36:18,440 --> 00:36:20,300
I need this hand to play the piano.

572
00:36:22,440 --> 00:36:23,640
I have to play Chopin

573
00:36:24,960 --> 00:36:25,760
and Liszt.

574
00:36:26,800 --> 00:36:28,660
I have to tour and release albums.

575
00:36:29,200 --> 00:36:31,730
I can't just let this hand be ruined like this.

576
00:36:32,880 --> 00:36:34,960
I understand all of this,

577
00:36:35,240 --> 00:36:36,400
but I'm truly sorry.

578
00:36:36,400 --> 00:36:37,660
We have tried our best.

579
00:36:37,960 --> 00:36:39,440
As I told you before,

580
00:36:39,440 --> 00:36:41,240
even the best medical skills or doctors

581
00:36:41,240 --> 00:36:43,360
can't guarantee that your hand

582
00:36:43,360 --> 00:36:45,760
will fully regain its previous functions.

583
00:36:45,800 --> 00:36:46,680
If you couldn't guarantee it,

584
00:36:46,680 --> 00:36:47,440
why did you

585
00:36:47,440 --> 00:36:49,170
waste so much of my time before?

586
00:36:49,800 --> 00:36:51,800
You misdiagnosed me, you know that?

587
00:36:51,800 --> 00:36:53,800
I can sue you for misdiagnosis.

588
00:36:53,800 --> 00:36:54,800
Mr. Chen, calm down.

589
00:36:54,800 --> 00:36:55,600
Do you know how much this hand

590
00:36:55,600 --> 00:36:57,120
means to me?

591
00:36:57,120 --> 00:36:58,160
Don't touch me.

592
00:37:01,040 --> 00:37:01,600
Mr. Chen.

593
00:37:13,200 --> 00:37:14,280
Thank you, kid.

594
00:37:18,280 --> 00:37:19,280
Thank you for introducing me

595
00:37:19,280 --> 00:37:20,640
to such a good doctor.

596
00:37:22,200 --> 00:37:22,840
Mr. Chen.

597
00:37:24,320 --> 00:37:25,760
I'm really sorry, Dr. Sun.

598
00:37:25,760 --> 00:37:27,020
Sorry for the trouble.

599
00:37:52,240 --> 00:37:54,200
Mr. Chen came for rehabilitation just now

600
00:37:54,200 --> 00:37:55,730
and had a fight with Dr. Sun.

601
00:37:57,080 --> 00:37:59,940
Mr. Chen might never be able to play the piano again.

602
00:38:01,520 --> 00:38:02,780
How could this happen?

603
00:38:03,280 --> 00:38:04,740
I'm not quite sure either.

604
00:38:06,240 --> 00:38:06,920
I saw

605
00:38:07,080 --> 00:38:08,440
Mr. Chen leave in anger.

606
00:38:09,560 --> 00:38:10,080
Aiwei.

607
00:38:11,040 --> 00:38:12,970
Mr. Chen is emotionally unstable.

608
00:38:13,280 --> 00:38:15,540
I'm very worried about his mental state.

609
00:38:15,960 --> 00:38:17,420
If you have any questions,

610
00:38:17,680 --> 00:38:19,540
you can contact me anytime, okay?

611
00:38:31,840 --> 00:38:34,040
He has a distal humerus fracture in his right arm,

612
00:38:34,040 --> 00:38:35,480
which injured his brachial artery.

613
00:38:35,480 --> 00:38:36,440
The delay in surgery

614
00:38:36,440 --> 00:38:39,040
caused ischemic muscle contracture of the entire arm.

615
00:38:39,040 --> 00:38:39,880
This may cause

616
00:38:40,080 --> 00:38:42,540
irreversible damage to his hand functions.

617
00:42:00,560 --> 00:42:02,090
I heard about it from Wu Han.

618
00:42:04,600 --> 00:42:05,400
Are you okay?

619
00:42:05,720 --> 00:42:07,560
I don't want to see you right now.
